_man_ - display manual pages

_man_ [*section*] *name1*...
_man_ -*i* [*section*]

 -*i*  display section index (default is all sections)
 
 *section*  manual section to search for name (*c* or *f*)
 *name1*... manual page name

The *MANCOLOR* environment variable controls whether to apply attibutes
to the output of the *man* command.

*MANCOLOR=1* enables attributed output, *MANCOLOR=2* enables ANSI colors,
and *MANCOLOR=0* forces plain text output.
